OL,6,FBBC South West managed to produce
OL,7,Flunchtime, early evening and late-
OL,8,Fevening editions of Spotlight on
OL,9,FWednesday.  BBC East Midlands Today
OL,10,Fwas broadcast at 6.30pm and 10.30pm
OL,11,Fon Wednesday.
OL,13,FBBC East Midlands Today also went out
OL,14,Fon BBC One West Midlands at 10.30pm.
OL,16,FOn local radio, some stations
OL,17,Fbroadcast a syndicated programme
OL,18,Fshortly after 11am. Others kept their
OL,19,Fown shows, although many used stand-
OL,20,Fin hosts.
